      "author": "wrenger",
      "description": "This release allows you to specify a language in a document:\r\n\r\nJust add the following key to the document properties (`crtl+;`):\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\nlt_language: en-US\r\n```\r\n\r\nNow, each of your documents can have a different language. This feature was proposed by @gvasco #4.\r\n\r\nThere is also a new command to accept all suggestions #11 and the error message for documents that are too large to be checked in one go by LanguageTool's public API are now much better #13.",
